ter each session</li>\n<li>Group sign-up through JTT/ATT scheduler, BOOK NOW location on this website</li>\n<li>Book your private virtual coaching with Jordan directly</li>\n</ul>\n\n[/accordion-item]\n\n[/accordion]\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'Remote Coaching', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'remote-coaching', '', '', '2022-01-25 00:12:43', '2022-01-25 00:12:43', '', 0, 'https://jordanyounggolf.com/?page_id=330', 0, 'page', '', 0),
